aces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02775f8ad4e32f9dbad8bfa53c2ba11a9de14fb","tid":475702,"uid":24160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"邊忽似23? 佢唔係九十後呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca621711fc6e51b43818f211902b21d8bec0e191","tid":475702,"uid":75156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個肥仔拎自己做版根本係以偏概全<br />\n有無理解過人地先<br />\n係你好撚命 遇著個咁抵得諗既老細<br />\n人地<span style=\"color: red;\">個</span>d 點解會變成做又三十六唔做又三十六既心態唔係生出黎就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而係</span>遇得多仆街又涼薄既工同同事，<br />\n幾抵得諗既人都變得斤斤計較啦傻閪<br />\n你<span style=\"color: red;\">好彩</span>上到岸就離地屌人啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好命依家野唔係出世做李家誠個孫<span style=\"color: red;\">先算係</span><br />\n你咁撚樣唔算好命算咩 <br />\n算努力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港幾撚多人都勤力 做撚爛晒市都係咁撚樣 無得升又無得加人工<br />\n個個有衝勁有志氣都磨撚蝕晒<br />\n大佬呀 <span style=\"color: red;\">自己既努力得到人賞識唔算好命算乜 好既有餐茶請你飲咪算係咁囉 比你入股真係唔知撞左咩神彩</span><br />\n係你咁好彩未沉個陣遇到個好老細同有位比你上啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4a3f22c5afc5feea59774bd67fea612c37836601","tid":475702,"uid":611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"荔枝角工廠區 三送飯連可樂無例湯外賣都50$ <br />\n中上環呢個價 有啖湯飲 有菜有肉 唔差呀"},{"pid":"b39bbc3ac15afd85033a2ac7edfeaa5c8e59b482","tid":475702,"uid":79427,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"做食唔好得罪人wor<br />\n<br />\n比人玩大把位入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a167e59b688c65b61e849d7d063de87cefcfcdd4","tid":475702,"uid":144312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>篇報道有講&quot;批評香港90後只懂去旅行，不懂儲錢買樓&quot;?</blockquote><br />\n我都